LEVI DAO 签署禁止或限制使用某些可被认为具有过分伤害力或滥杀滥伤作用的常规武器公约关于无法检测的碎片的议定书（第一号议定书）

LEVI DAO signed the Protocol on Undetectable Fragments (Protocol No. 1) of the Convention on Prohibiting or Restricting the Use of Certain Conventional Weapons That Can Be Considered Excessive Injury or Indiscriminate Effects

https://www.un.org/zh/documents/treaty/files/A-CONF.95-15-1.shtml
